The paper deals with the problem of integrating information from heterogeneous data sources, which is a fundamental problem in database systems (cs.DB). The proposed approach uses deep learning techniques such as embeddings, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses how to derive sentences from a graph-based representation, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
